### 1. Создаем деталь на Складе (Масло моторное, 100 литров по 500 руб)
POST http://localhost:8080/odata/v4/RepairService/Stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "3f7b2c91-1d64-46bb-8f04-12f0a0011004",
  "name": "Premium 5W-30 Synthetic Engine Oil",
  "type": "Original",
  "quantity": 100,
  "price": 25.00,
  "currency_code": "USD"
}

### 2. Создаем услугу в Справочнике работ (Замена масла, 1000 руб/час)
POST http://localhost:8080/odata/v4/RepairService/ServicesOffered
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "5b91d7c3-8a42-4f6e-9c01-12f0a0012001",
  "name": "Standard Oil and Filter Replacement",
  "standardHour": 1.0,
  "price": 50.00,
  "currency_code": "USD"
}

### 3. Создаем пустую Заявку (Мастер-запись)
POST http://localhost:8080/odata/v4/RepairService/Appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "9f1c2d68-1a6b-4e9a-8db5-4f0c3b2a1001",
  "appointmentNo": "APT-1001",
  "carNumber": "A123BC",
  "status": "New"
}

### 4. Добавляем 4 литра масла в заявку
POST http://localhost:8080/odata/v4/RepairService/Appointments(9f1c2d68-1a6b-4e9a-8db5-4f0c3b2a1001)/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Part",
  "quantity": 4,
  "stockItem_ID": "3f7b2c91-1d64-46bb-8f04-12f0a0011004"
}

### 5. ПРОВЕРКА: Смотрим итоговую сумму заявки
GET http://localhost:8080/odata/v4/RepairService/Appointments(9f1c2d68-1a6b-4e9a-8db5-4f0c3b2a1001)